snippet.title: Enjoy Fast-Paced Battles in Pokémon Rumble World!
snippet.description:
http://bit.ly/1FfW4wE
Exciting battles await in Pokémon Rumble World! This new, downloadable game features cute, controllable Toy Pokémon to battle and befriend. Learn more about this free-to-download game for the Nintendo 3DS family of systems on our site! 

Official site: http://www.pokemon.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Pokemon
Twitter: http://twitter.com/Pokemon
